{"tid":823144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺災後返工返學問題上，香港竟不如台灣","createTime":"2018-09-16T16:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T05:17:18.000Z","uid":109462,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d643e69ace005c9a593cb91ed2c1b27a908a212e","tid":823144,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"中華民國《天然災害停止上班及上課作業辦法》<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>第 4 條\t<br />\n風災已達下列基準之一者，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">得發布停止上班及上課：</span></strong><br />\n一、依據氣象預報，颱風暴風半徑於四小時內可能經過之地區，其平均風力可達七級以上或陣風可達十級以上時。<br />\n二、依據氣象預報或實際觀測，降雨量達附表之各通報權責機關停止上班上課雨量參考基準，且已致災或有致災之虞時。<br />\n三、風力或降雨量未達前二款停止上班及上課基準之地區，因受地形、雨量影響，致交通、水電供應中斷或供應困難，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">影響通行、上班上課安全或有致災之虞時。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?PCode=S0110022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flaw.moj.gov.tw%2FLawClass%2FLawAll.aspx%3FPCode%3DS0110022&d=Ca0vyMdcXwcQhBZMct%2BZAZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bdb57bb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?PCode=S0110022</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中華民國《天然災害發生事業單位勞工出勤管理及工資給付要點》<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>六、天然災害發生時（後），有下列情形之一者，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雇主不得視為曠工、遲到或強迫勞工以事假或其他假別處理，且不得強迫勞工補行工作、扣發全勤獎金、解僱或為其他不利之處分：</span></strong><br />\n（一）勞工工作所在地經轄區首長依「天然災害停止辦公及上課作業辦法」（以下稱作業辦法）規定通報停止辦公，勞工因而未出勤時。<br />\n（二）勞工工作所在地未經轄區首長依作業辦法規定通報停止辦公，惟勞工確因颱風、洪水、地震等因素阻塞交通致延遲到工或未能出勤時。<br />\n（三）勞工工作所在地未經轄區首長依作業辦法規定通報停止辦公，惟其居住地區或其正常上（下）班必經地區，經該管轄區首長依作業辦法規定通報停止辦公，致未出勤時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://laws.mol.gov.tw/FLAW/FLAWDAT0202.aspx?lsid=FL049533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flaws.mol.gov.tw%2FFLAW%2FFLAWDAT0202.aspx%3Flsid%3DFL049533&d=Ca0vyMdcXwcQhBZMct%2BZAZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bc8e1197\" target=\"_blank\">https://laws.mol.gov.tw/FLAW/FLAWDAT0202.aspx?lsid=FL049533</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6b4f1802f06348ec2a61ce4956dcce460458edc5","tid":823144,"uid":109462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:19:06.000Z","msg":"反觀香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>【山竹襲港】天文台:明早六時前考慮改發3號強風信號<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1319139/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1319139%2F&d=Ca0vyMdcXwcQhBZMct%2BZAZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6b43263a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1319139%2F&h=fa3708ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1319139/</a><br />\n<br />\n特首籲僱主體諒僱員恢復上班後或遇困難 冀彈性處理<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/instant/5b9e6649e60383bb17205b77\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Finstant%2F5b9e6649e60383bb17205b77&d=Ca0vyMdcXwcQhBZMct%2BZAZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=708aa59a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/instant/5b9e6649e60383bb17205b77</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"abf3cf30ea01db47d130440b1652bb31cde51f2b","tid":823144,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/124/162/124162d3e189ec7e5c143bdf92ee6659606688c5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F124%2F162%2F124162d3e189ec7e5c143bdf92ee6659606688c5_b.jpg&h=fdf496a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16203e1a671439c4c21196bb7772c2370d16ec7b","tid":823144,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"返工返學關乎到搵錢，香港自豪賺得錢多就一定係咁，有乜咁奇? 唔通靠創科局?"},{"pid":"d2eb2d21397d13f52b100e8140ca887a27bd472e","tid":823144,"uid":28028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"香港人患比天災<br />\n嚴重得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a573b47e6511a179f02416a111b34efb80def4","tid":823144,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote